images.title: How do you say 'gnarly' in Nazaré?
images.caption: Nazaré Lighthouse
images.desc: Instead of Surfin' USA, today we're Surfin' Portugal—though if you shout a reverential 'cowabunga' at these colossal waves, we're sure the locals will get your meaning.
